{"tid":586592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳家珮向區諾軒發律師信","createTime":"2018-03-09T15:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T10:55:35.000Z","uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5a24c5c4b1d0d2d4e4696d0dcbcfbf4648bb0578","tid":586592,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"陳家珮 Judy Chan<br />\n8 mins &middot; <br />\n【陳家珮選舉辦公室聲明】<br />\n<br />\n留意到立法會補選(港島區) 1 號候選人區諾軒，於今天在其面書上載了【致 陳家珮 Judy Chan 公開信】以及【捍衛人治，回歸黨性】兩則帖文，後者更竄改了4號候選人陳家珮「捍衛法治，回歸理性」的競選口號。<br />\n<br />\n經詳細閱讀及研究後，我們認為區諾軒先生觸犯了香港法例第554章《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》。陳家珮的選舉代理人曾向群先生晚上已向廉政公署舉報，明天陳家珮的代表律師將會向區諾軒先生發出律師信，指出他可能干犯香港法例第554章《選舉(舞弊及非法行為)條例》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JudyChanKaPui/posts/810164362508638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJudyChanKaPui%2Fposts%2F810164362508638&d=RCy%2F34UwP%2Bv8XPXFD%2BhNptr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f8b5196f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JudyChanKaPui/posts/810164362508638</a><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c664f601e2fb97531318dd7cb4a1819a169c5b1","tid":586592,"uid":1712,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"3ae28a642868b0bb5645c2b31923736e6da13413","tid":586592,"uid":91463,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:05:15.000Z","msg":"呢條死賤畜列人地7宗罪抹黑人就得<br />\n正宗死賤種"},{"pid":"f72ac598d409148abfd4983c352f4c2d8318ab9d","tid":586592,"uid":18385,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"怨婦"},{"pid":"889c82a8d60157df3a79552eee7492648b64c75e","tid":586592,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T16:12:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cb94d8cd035ef3